sequenceDiagram
  participant User
  participant CLI
  participant Parsers
  participant Normalizers
  participant Merger
  participant Validator
  participant Export

  User->>CLI: run with inputs
  CLI->>Parsers: parse CSV/resume/LinkedIn
  Parsers->>Normalizers: raw objects
  Normalizers->>Merger: normalized objects
  Merger->>Validator: canonical profile
  Validator->>Export: write JSON
